{"tid":1578831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"畜龍偷食大陸妹, 千奇唔好搵人話俾佢女朋友知（2）","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T11:54:23.000Z","uid":168677,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"efc6637103ff95d43460a2a6e4ff5f42b327d563","tid":1578831,"uid":168677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚睇睇下老豆搵仔, 喂見到有個人咁熟口面, 原來係8月出Trip成都嗰時係酒店撞到過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cj0Kkhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcj0Kkhc.jpg&h=e036719e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpSpkhd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxpSpkhd.jpg&h=19a6cd5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌第一日住已經覺得有班狗樣大隻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問下人先知世警會。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會咁留意呢隻犬隻, 係因為佢日日早餐拖住個四眼大陸妹, 而個大陸妹條紅色連身裙著咗足足3日, 係3日啊屌! 外賣雞3日都唔換衫~~ 係咪貪平啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時都話呢個世界真係好細, 畜龍原來準備11月結婚, 好想話俾佢女朋友知叫佢body Check咗先好結啊~~~~~~~~~~~~~有無人識當時人啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結定唔結 諗清楚先好結<br />\n<br />\n酒店 樓層證據 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9pi9Zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9pi9Zk.png&h=578660a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHWYqxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHWYqxG.jpg&h=ca4e83fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gkm17L1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkm17L1.jpg&h=3c074f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可<br />\n#黑警死全家<br />\n#黑警填命"},{"pid":"b159e9cacb86c2c43c3088927b319a9cfc00059a","tid":1578831,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e73818cb395fb6bec7bcc404f22a01f6497bf82","tid":1578831,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf99e2f788748ee506f89cf1db9833c17f7d0565","tid":1578831,"uid":168677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"唔好再推呢個post啦"},{"pid":"4d99af213c0dd0012babd23b8c49d4df2e150a6e","tid":1578831,"uid":255779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"記得驗身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c6679df8600f2a50245044197c2560fc739ae2","tid":1578831,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"嘩屌啲狗真係好撚污糟"},{"pid":"0979a038b268f5d3c229cdf95e65dcb3f3bca943","tid":1578831,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"應該無愛滋病，無花既"},{"pid":"d96844e0f7e54b6ca